QUESTION:
Find out the names of the ships in the Ships table that meet at least four criteria from the following list:
numGuns = 8,
bore = 15,
displacement = 32000,
type = bb,
launched = 1915,
class = Kongo,
country = USA.

SOLUTION:
SELECT s.name
FROM Ships s JOIN Classes c ON s.class = c.class
WHERE
CASE WHEN numGuns = 8 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
     + CASE WHEN bore = 15 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
     + CASE WHEN displacement = 32000 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
     + CASE WHEN type = 'bb' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
     + CASE WHEN launched = 1915 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
     + CASE WHEN c.class = 'Kongo' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
     + CASE WHEN country = 'USA' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
     > = 4
